'''Create Force Wraith''' was the [[Force power/Legends|Force power]] which allowed Force-users to create [[Force Wraith]]s. Because of the nature of this power, creating a being of [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] energies, the user was seduced more and more by the dark side each time they used it.

